<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1158752-did-you-ever-read-robert-penn-warren-s">Did you ever read Robert Penn Warren&#39;s &quot;All the Kings&quot; I was loosely based on Huey P. Long, Senator and Governor of Louisiana? Another great political novel was &quot;The Last Hurrah&quot; about &quot;Honey Fitz&quot; Fitzgerald, one of the early political Kennedys and long-serving mayor&#39;s of Boston.</a>
</div>
