<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes. Yes I did. Although I remember it as &quot;All the king&apos;s men&quot; as per the nursery rhyme of Humpty Dumpty<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes. Yes I did. Although I remember it as "All the king's men" as per the nursery rhyme of Humpty Dumpty<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
